text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits IRM 4.9.2, Examination Technical Time Reporting System, Description and Use of Examination Technical Time Report-Form 4502, which has been made obsolete.

The content from IRM 4.9.2, Description and Use of Examination Technical Time Report-Form 4502, dated April 1, 2004 is obsolete. The information in this IRM has been incorporated into IRM 4.9.1, Examination Technical Time Reporting System, Outline of System, because the subject matter was very similar and most of the information in IRM 4.9.2 was obsolete.
